/#
 The specification of how an FX OTC option strike price is quoted.
 #/
enum FpML5.transparency.StrikeQuoteBasisEnum {
    # The strike price is an amount of putCurrency per one unit of callCurrency.
    PutCurrencyPerCallCurrency 
    # The strike price is an amount of callCurrency per one unit of putCurrency.
    CallCurrencyPerPutCurrency 

}

PutCurrencyPerCallCurrency.Doc: The strike price is an amount of putCurrency per one unit of callCurrency.
PutCurrencyPerCallCurrency.Name: PutCurrencyPerCallCurrency

CallCurrencyPerPutCurrency.Doc: The strike price is an amount of callCurrency per one unit of putCurrency.
CallCurrencyPerPutCurrency.Name: CallCurrencyPerPutCurrency
